               <person instant="false"><!--donor-->
                  <persName corresp="PRS0000" instant="false" full="yes">The original donor is most probably Rǝstä (?) Maryam (s. fol. 34vb) initially mentioned in supplication formulas. His wife Wälättä Krǝstos (e.g., fol. 17rb), his daughter Wälättä Dǝngǝl (e.g., fol. 15vb) as well as ʿAqbä Krǝstos with his wife ʿƎṣä Ḥǝywät (e.g, fol. 18ra) are also mentioned.&#xD;
However, their names were mostly erased and replaced with that of Zǝkrä Maryam (fol. 6ra) or Wälättä Mikaʾel and Wälättä Ṣǝyon (fol. 19vb). &#xD;
&#xD;
Śärḍä Dǝngǝl, Wälättä ʾƎleni and Gǝddä Maryam are mentioned in the supplication formulas in Text I-1 (fols. 1vb, 5ra).</persName>
